  "texts": [
    "Examples of functional monitoring include:(a) Accuracy monitoring: Evaluating the AI system's ability to produce correct outputs or predictions.",
    "(b) Efficiency monitoring: Assessing the system's resource utilization, such as processing time and memory consumption.",
    "(c) Reliability monitoring: Examining the AI system's consistency and stability over time and in varying conditions.",
    "Safety monitoringSafety monitoring focuses on identifying and mitigating potential risks associated with the AI system's operation.",
    "This type of monitoring is essential for preventing harm to users, other systems, or the environment."
  ],
